item.title: Server models help!
item.dc:creator: @strengthpk strengthpk
item.description:
@strengthpk wrote:

Lol you don’t add models to server… it’s client sided… go to your models folder add the models… go to class.8 on your client folders and add the ints… AND then go to your server item folder and go under whatever it is platebody etc. and add the id # that will unglitch it.
